<l>aṭaṅkeḻil campat taṭaṅkakkaṇ ṭīca</l>
<l>ṉaṭaṅkeḻi laḵteṉ ṟaṭaṅkuka vuḷḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Submissively seeing the wealth of comprised beauty,</l>
<l>saying “that is the beauty comprised in the lord” may you yield, oh mind.</l>
      </lg>
